  <brief_title>Role of Lung Ultrasound in Confirmation of Correct Double Lumen Endotracheal Tube Placement in Thoracic Surgeries</brief_title>
  <official_title>Role of Transthoracic Lung Ultrasound in Confirmation of Correct Double Lumen Endotracheal Tube</official_title>
