  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      to assess the efficacy of lung ultrasound versus conventional auscultation method and&#xD;
      fiberoptic bronchoscopy in confirmation of double lumen tube position&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Confirmation of double lumen tube position by auscultation followed fiberoptic bronchoscopy&#xD;
      then lung ultrasound. After double lumen intubation all patient tube position will be&#xD;
      confirmed using auscultation then fiberoptic bronchoscopy then lung ultrasound&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
